prompt:
A mesmerizing and vivid digital painting featuring an enchanting oasis at its center. 
The oasis is a stunning gradient of colors, transitioning from deep blue hues to bright oranges, creating a surreal and serene atmosphere. 
Surrounding the oasis are intricately designed and uniquely colored crystal flowers, each adding a touch of beauty and charm to the scene. 
The background is a simple, clean white, allowing the oasis and flowers to stand out and captivate the viewer's attention. 
The large word 'OASIS Sync - v0\.3\.4 -' is seamlessly integrated into the artwork using a double exposure effect, adding an artistic touch and showcasing the evolution of the piece. 
The overall composition is a harmonious blend of nature and art, with the oasis serving as the focal point amidst the detailed and vibrant background.
